Who We Are


Stellex Capital Management LP is a private equity firm that invests in middle-market companies in North America and Europe through its offices in New York and London.  We seek to identify opportunities where we can deploy capital to provide stability, catalyze operational improvement and foster growth.  We work closely with high quality management teams to unlock and enhance the value of the underlying franchise.


























