Stellex Capital Management LP Key Developments

Columbus Castings Reportedly To Be Sold
May 18 16
Columbus Castings Company may be sold to a new buyer after Constellation Enterprises LLC filed for Chapter 11. Some Stellex officials are at the plant preparing for a possible sale, according to people familiar with the situation. Stellex Capital Management LP  is the potential buyer, according to sources. Spokesmen for both Stellex and Columbus Castings said they had no comment on the identity of the buyer.


